---
import BlogLayout from '../../layouts/BlogLayout.astro';
---

<BlogLayout title="Albums - Page 3">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">Oasis Albums</h1>

    <div class="space-y-12">
      <article class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg">
       

<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4"><a href="https://oasisreunion.live/heathen-chemistry/" class="hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors">Heathen Chemistry (2002)</a></h2>



        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Album Statistics</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6">
              <li>Release Date: July 1, 2002</li>
              <li>UK Chart Position: #1</li>
              <li>First Week Sales: 270,000 copies</li>
              <li>Total Sales: Over 3.4 million copies worldwide</li>
              <li>Certification: 2× Platinum (UK)</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Key Tracks</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6">
              <li>The Hindu Times</li>
              <li>Stop Crying Your Heart Out</li>
              <li>Little By Little</li>
              <li>Songbird</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-4">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Songwriting Credits</h3>
          <p>The first Oasis album to feature songwriting contributions from all band members, including Liam Gallagher's first solo composition "Songbird".</p>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Don't Believe the Truth (2005)</h2>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Album Statistics</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6">
              <li>Release Date: May 30, 2005</li>
              <li>UK Chart Position: #1</li>
              <li>First Week Sales: 237,000 copies</li>
              <li>Total Sales: Over 7 million copies worldwide</li>
              <li>Certification: 2× Platinum (UK)</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Key Tracks</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6">
              <li>Lyla</li>
              <li>The Importance of Being Idle</li>
              <li>Let There Be Love</li>
              <li>Turn Up the Sun</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-4">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Critical Reception</h3>
          <p>Widely considered their strongest album since Be Here Now, receiving positive reviews for its more collaborative approach and return to form.</p>
        </div>
      </article>

      <div class="flex justify-between mt-8">
        <a href="/albums/2" class="inline-block bg-black text-white px-6 py-2 rounded hover:bg-gray-800">
          ← Previous Page
        </a>
        <a href="/albums/4" class="inline-block bg-black text-white px-6 py-2 rounded hover:bg-gray-800">
          Next Page →
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BlogLayout>
